<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <% include 'head.ect' %>
        <title>SDMS Welcome</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="col-flex" style="height:100%">
            <div class="header" style="flex:none">
                <div class="row-flex">
                    <div style="flex:1;font-size: 2em">Scientific Data Management System - Welcome!</div><div style="flex:none;display:flex;justify-content:flex-end"><button class="btn" onclick="location.href='/ui/login'">Log-In / Register</button></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="content" class="ui-widget-content" style="padding:2em;flex:1 1 100%">
                <h1>About</h1>
                <p>This is the SDMS welcome/landing page for anonymous users. A brief introduction will be provided with links for registration and logging in. If a user has recently authenticated, this page will be bypassed, and the user will instead go to the SDMS main page.</p>
                <h2>Requirements</h2>
                <p>A Globus Online account with a linked Globus ID identity is required to access the SDMS. If you do not have a Globus Online account, or have not yet linked a Globus ID identity, please sign-up (for free) at <a href="https://www.globusid.org/">GlobusID.org</a> then return to this page to register for SDMS access.</p>
                <h2>Globus Automation</h2>
                <p>The SDMS utilizes Globus for automated file transfers on behalf of SDMS users (i.e. from jobs scipts, worklows, or applications). During registration, new users wil be redirected to a Globus authorization page where appropriate permissions must be granted to the SDMS in order for automated file transfers to function.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="footer" style="flex:none">
                User: Not Logged In
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
    <script>
        $(".btn").button();
    </script>
</html>
